OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780989358
OL,3,C'Hold health professionals to account'
OL,4,Cover way Grace's killer was managed
OL,6,FThe parents of Grace O'Malley-Kumar
OL,7,Fsaid health professionals should be
OL,8,Fheld to account over the way her
OL,9,Fkiller was managed.
OL,11,FValdo Calocane was detained under
OL,12,Fmental health laws four times until he
OL,13,Fwas discharged in 2022.
OL,15,FGrace, from Woodford Green, was
OL,16,Fstudying in Nottingham when she was
OL,17,Fkilled by Calocane three years ago.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
