FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780989358
OL,3,C'Hold health professionals to account'
OL,4,Cover way Grace's killer was managed
OL,6,FThe inquiry into the attacks, which
OL,7,Fheard from 164 witnesses, finished on
OL,8,FFriday and is expected to report back
OL,9,Fwith recommendations next year.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News London Grace's
OL,12,Ffather Dr Sanjoy Kumar said: "Well,
OL,13,FSinead (Grace's mother) and I are
OL,14,Fdoctors and we worked in the NHS for a
OL,15,Fcombined of about 60 years.
OL,17,F"We understand the systems that failed
OL,18,Fand we've been able to highlight those
OL,19,Fto this inquiry.
OL,26,@uD@HpmuD@Wpn
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780989358
OL,3,C'Hold health professionals to account'
OL,4,Cover way Grace's killer was managed
OL,6,F"At a personal level, I must have sent
OL,7,Fhundreds and hundreds of questions at
OL,8,Fevery juncture where we thought that
OL,9,Fthere was a missed opportunity and we
OL,10,Fhaven't had answers to those yet.
OL,12,F"But the point being is that we need
OL,13,Fchanges, we need people to be
OL,14,Faccountable.
OL,16,F"As a family, we are holding them to
OL,17,Faccount because we understand those
OL,18,Fsystems better than perhaps others.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780989358
OL,3,C'Hold health professionals to account'
OL,4,Cover way Grace's killer was managed
OL,6,F"And that's why it's given us an
OL,7,Fopportunity to say in detail, these
OL,8,Fare where the failures were and why
OL,9,Fdid this happen?"
OL,11,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar and Barnaby
OL,12,FWebber, both 19, and 65-year-old
OL,13,Fschool caretaker Ian Coates were
OL,14,Fkilled by Calocane.
OL,16,FThe triple killer then used a van he
OL,17,Fstole from Mr Coates to try to murder
OL,18,Fthree people in Nottingham city centre.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
